data.description: Welcome to this fabulous rare Southwest Gem in the well kept Palm Valley Community. Ask About The VA Assumable Loan at 2.625% for a VA Approved Buyer. It has updated wood tile in all bedrooms and living/dining room. Extra large patio. Newer appliances in the Kitchen and an open floor plan makes this home feel bigger than it really is. Master Bedroom has separate tub & shower and spacious walk in closet. there are vertical blinds through the home and the cabinets are all upgraded maple. A soft water loop is available and there is a gas stub for barbecue and dryer. The garage is extended by 4 feet and Backyard is very private with no homes directly behind it Oooh là là!!!! Priced to Sell Hurry Before This One is Gone!!!!!!!!!!!
